net.dean.jraw.paginators

Class Paginator<T extends Thing>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.dean.jraw.paginators.Paginator<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type that the listings will contain
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<Listing<T>>, RedditIterable<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DuplicatesPaginator, GenericPaginator, LiveThreadPaginator, ModLogPaginator, MultiHubPaginator, MultiRedditPaginator, RelatedPaginator, SpecificPaginator, SubmissionSearchPaginator, SubredditPaginator, SubredditSearchPaginator

    public abstract class Paginator<T extends Thing>
extends java.lang.Object
implements RedditIterable<T>
    Provides the ability to iterate through data provided by the Reddit API.

      • RECOMMENDED_MAX_LIMIT

        public static final int RECOMMENDED_MAX_LIMIT
        The recommended maximum limit of Things to return. No client-side code is in place to ensure that the limit is not set over this number, but the Reddit API will only return this many amount of objects.
